/* =========================================================================
   Persona Compendium detail data — Phase 1 (v3.7.1 scaffold)
   -------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Per-persona battle detail for the Registry's expandable cards. Keyed by
   the EXACT registry name from personaData.js (accents included — "Arsène").
   personaData.js itself is never modified (hard rule: no game-data value
   alterations; registry names are also the p_<name> check-key source).

   Approved schema (owner sign-off 2026-07-04):
     {
       stats: { st, ma, en, ag, lu },        // base stats at base level
       affinities: {                         // AFFINITY_ORDER, tokens below
         phys, gun, fire, ice, elec,
         wind, psy, nuke, bless, curse
       },
       skills: [ { name, lvl } ],            // learned-by-leveling only;
                                             // lvl === base level ⇒ innate
       trait: "…"                            // Royal trait
     }

   Phase 2 (deferred, fields reserved — do not add yet): itemization
   { normal, alarm }.

   Population is done by scripts/ingest-persona-details.mjs and gated by
   scripts/check-persona-details.mjs (npm run check:details, also in CI).
   Stat authority: JP allchart (hard rule) — disputes resolve to it.
   ========================================================================= */

